{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Layout instructions for dev
    
    Desktop layout
    
    Full width section near the end of the FAQ page.
    
    Background: light neutral (for example, very soft beige or off white).
    
    Two columns:
    
    Left column: text block + contact button.
    
    Right column: optional image block.
    
    Vertical alignment: center content in both columns.
    
    Padding: generous padding on all sides so it feels calm and spacious.
    
    Mobile layout
    
    Stack content in one column.
    
    Order:
    
    Optional image (full width, rounded corners).
    
    Heading and paragraph.
    
    Contact info list.
    
    Contact button (full width).
    
    Maintain comfortable spacing between each element.
    
    Image slot
    
    Optional.
    
    Accepts one image.
    
    On desktop: right column, fixed max width, auto height, rounded corners.
    
    On mobile: full width, aspect ratio around 4:3 or 3:2.
    
    Button behaviour
    
    Primary button under the text and contact info.
    
    On click:
    
    Open WhatsApp chat if on mobile.
    
    Or go to a dedicated Contact page / open mail link, depending on your setup.
    
    Button label: “Contact SO. by Sora”., amazing lets add Adderss in contact information
